              "id": "844356cb-170d-4599-93b5-36601aeacda7",
              "name": "jobDescription",
              "value": "We are hiring a Full Stack MERN Developer.\n\nRequired Skills:\n- React\n- Node.js\n- Express.js\n- MongoDB\n- JavaScript\n- REST API\n- Git\n\nPreferred Skills:\n- Docker\n- AWS\n\nExperience:\n2+ years\n\nEducation:\nBachelor's Degree in Computer Science or related field.",
