    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Analyze the candidate resume below.\n\nResume:\n{{ $json.text }}\n\n\nJob Description:\n\n{{ $json.jobDescription }}\nReturn ONLY valid JSON.\n\n1. Analyze both the Job Description and Candidate Resume thoroughly.\n2. Extract the candidate's information from the resume.\n3. Compare the candidate's qualifications with the job requirements.\n4. Evaluate:\n   - Technical Skills\n   - Soft Skills\n   - Experience\n   - Education\n   - Certifications\n   - Projects\n   - Domain Knowledge\n   - Tools & Technologies\n5. Identify:\n   - Matching Skills\n   - Missing Skills\n   - Additional Skills\n6. Calculate an ATS Matching Score between 0 and 100.\n7. Explain why the candidate received that score.\n8. Recommend whether the candidate should move to the next hiring round.\n\n## ATS Score Guidelines\n\n90-100 = Excellent Match\n80-89 = Strong Match\n70-79 = Good Match\n60-69 = Average Match\nBelow 60 = Poor Match\n\n## Return ONLY valid JSON.\n\nDo NOT use markdown.\nDo NOT include explanations outside the JSON.\nDo NOT wrap the JSON inside ```json.\n\nReturn exactly in the following format:\n\n{\n  \"candidateName\": \"\",\n  \"email\": \"\",\n  \"phone\": \"\",\n  \"location\": \"\",\n  \"totalExperience\": \"\",\n  \"education\": [],\n  \"certifications\": [],\n  \"technicalSkills\": [],\n  \"softSkills\": [],\n  \"projects\": [],\n  \"matchingSkills\": [],\n  \"missingSkills\": [],\n  \"additionalSkills\": [],\n  \"experienceMatch\": \"\",\n  \"educationMatch\": \"\",\n  \"skillsMatch\": \"\",\n  \"projectRelevance\": \"\",\n  \"strengths\": [],\n  \"weaknesses\": [],\n  \"atsScore\": 0,\n  \"recommendation\": \"\",\n  \"summary\": \"\",\n  \"decision\": \"\"\n}\n\nDecision Rules:\n- ATS Score >= 80 → Shortlisted\n- ATS Score 60-79 → Consider\n- ATS Score < 60 → Rejected\n\nEnsure the ATS score is realistic and based on the actual comparison between the Job Description and Resume.",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are an expert HR Recruitment AI. Analyze the candidate resume against the job description and return ONLY valid JSON with the requested fields."
        }
      },
      "id": "5c278cdf-04d4-48a3-bec0-ecb05e6d25a8",
      "name": "AI Agent",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
